      "subtasks": [],
      "created": "2018-10-09T23:48:34.674+0000",
      "description": "The current implementation of container-executor accepts nm-local-dirs and nm-log-dirs from cli arguments.  If yarn user is compromised, it is possible for rogue yarn user to use container-executor to point nm-local-dirs to user home directory to make modification to user owned files.  This JIRA is to enhance container-executor.cfg to allow specification of yarn.nodemanager.local-dirs to safe guard rogue yarn user from exploiting nm-local-dirs paths.",
